 "html": "{%- set employee = frappe.get_doc(\"Employee\", doc.grievance_against) -%}\n{%- set designation = frappe.get_doc(\"Designation\", employee.designation) -%}\n \n<div class=\"page-break\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%!important;\">\n    <tr>\n        <!-- Kolom gambar kiri --> \n        <td style=\"width: 20%; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle;\">\n            <img src=\"/files/logo-sth-print-format.jpg\" \n                 style=\"height: 5rem; object-fit: contain;\"/>\n        </td>\n\n        <!-- Kolom teks tengah -->\n        <td style=\"width: 60%; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle!important;\">\n            <h1 style=\"color: green; font-weight: bold;\">{{ employee.company or '' }}</h1>\n        </td>\n\n        <!-- Kolom kosong kanan (biar teks tetap di tengah) -->\n        <td style=\"width: 20%;\"></td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n<div>\n    <h2 class=\"text-center\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">SURAT PERINGATAN 1</h2>\n    <hr style=\"border: 1px solid black; margin: 0!important;\">\n    <h5 class=\"text-center\">NO: {{doc.name}}</h5>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <p>Diberikan Kepada:</p>\n    <table>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">Nama Karyawan</td>\n            <td>:</td>\n            <td>{{employee.employee_name or '-'}}</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">NIK</td>\n            <td>:</td>\n            <td>{{employee.no_ktp or '-'}}</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">Jabatan</td>\n            <td>:</td>\n            <td>{{designation.designation_name or '-'}}</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">Hari dan tanggal diberikan SP</td>\n            <td>:</td>\n            <td>{{doc.get_formatted(\"date\") or '-'}}</td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <h3>1. Dasar Pelanggaran</h3>\n    <table style=\"width: 100%;\">\n        <tr>\n            <td style=\"border: 1px solid #000;\">{{doc.description or ''}}</td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div>\n<div>\n    <h3>2. Tindak Kedisiplinan</h3>\n    <p>Berdasarkan hal tersebut pada tanggal {{doc.get_formatted(\"date\")}}, maka diberikan tindakan sebagai berikut:</p>\n    <p>Sifat pelanggaran tersebut adalah: {{doc.custom_nature_of_violation or '-'}}</p>\n    </br>\n    <!--<table>-->\n    <!--    <tr>-->\n    <!--        <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">( ) Minor</td>-->\n    <!--        <td>( ) Moderat</td>-->\n    <!--        <td>( ) Serius</td>-->\n    <!--    </tr>-->\n    <!--</table>-->\n    <p>Sesuai dengan peraturan disiplin yang berlaku dalam Peraturan Perusahaan, maka Saudara diberikan: {{doc.subject or '-'}}</p>\n    </br>\n    <!--<table>-->\n    <!--    <tr>-->\n    <!--        <td style=\"padding-left: 0!important;\">( ) Peringatan I</td>-->\n    <!--        <td>( ) Peringatan II</td>-->\n    <!--        <td>( ) Peringatan III</td>-->\n    <!--    </tr>-->\n    <!--</table>-->\n    <p>Jenis sanksi pelanggaaran disiplin diberikan:</p>\n    <ul style=\"padding-left: 0; list-style: none;\">\n        <li>- Penilaian KPI</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 2rem;\">Surat Peringatan ini dikeluarkan oleh:</p>\n    (<span class=\"ttd_line\" style=\"margin-top: 6rem;\"></span>)\n    <p>\n        {%- set resolved = frappe.db.get_value(\"Employee\", {\"user_id\": doc.resolved_by}, \"employee_name\") -%}\n        Cc: {{resolved or doc.resolved_by}}\n    </p>\n</div>\n</div>",
